***---> readme file for the hello2.c <---***

This MPI program is an enhancment on hello1.c.

Hello2 will ceck its rank, and if the process is the master
then send a "Hello World!" message, in characters, to each 
of the workers. 

If the process is a worker, then receive the "Hello World!" 
message and print it out. 

Look over the function calls in hello1.c for help.

